Author Bio

Wujie Gu (Gavin) 顾悟杰
Creator of the WLM architecture.
Responsible for the structural design, dimensional logic, and protocol‑layer specification.
Not involved in engineering, implementation, or model development.
All technical integration must be performed by partner institutions using their own systems.

